So Guy's Golden Touch is not
whatever I touch turns to gold.

00:25:22.140 --> 00:25:24.060
Oh, god, I wish that were true.

00:25:24.060 --> 00:25:25.360
I wish that were true.

00:25:25.360 --> 00:25:30.810
Guy's Golden Touch is
whatever is gold, Guy touches.

00:25:30.810 --> 00:25:32.760
So find something great.

00:25:32.760 --> 00:25:34.170
Find something great.

00:25:34.170 --> 00:25:36.090
Reduce the friction.

00:25:36.090 --> 00:25:37.710
Learn to suck up.

00:25:37.710 --> 00:25:40.410
Get it into that upper
right-hand corner.

00:25:40.410 --> 00:25:42.390
Build an ecosystem around it.

00:25:42.390 --> 00:25:45.210
Don't take negativity.

00:25:45.210 --> 00:25:46.540
And change the world.

00:25:46.540 --> 00:25:48.810
And that's the
art of evangelism.

00:25:48.810 --> 00:25:50.990
